<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.5.5">
<l>cōtteṉa niṉṉait toḻuvaṉ varantara</l>
<l>pēycci mulaiyuṇṭa piḷḷāy periyaṉa</l>
<l>vāycciya rappam taruva ravarkkākac</l>
<l>cāṟṟiyō rāyiram cappāṇi</l>
<l rend="indent">taṭaṅkaika ḷālkoṭṭāy cappāṇi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Child who ate of the demoness’ breasts,</l>
<l>I prey to you, saying, ‘Hail,’ to grant [my] request.</l>
<l>The herder women will give [you] huge cakes.</l>
<l>For their sake, striking one-thousand [times], clap your hands;</l>
<l rend="indent">clap with your broad hands!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
